हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Rohan, who has been passionate about cooking since childhood, dreams of becoming a great chef despite growing up in poverty. He believes all he needs is a chance to showcase his talent. An unexpected twist enters his life with the Royal Hotel. Will Master Chef Anirudh, who works there, be in a position to give Rohan a chance? Who will emerge as the winner in this game among the chefs?
